Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.77,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仅凭那种路数根本就无法追及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.99,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
