Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:10.82,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就以属于自己的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:17.07,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以最后的一步决定世界的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.05,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯一的赢家非我莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.58,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已经亲眼见证了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:30.67,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁都无从预知的最佳答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:35.59,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是在棋盘上操纵一切的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.21,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}掀起思考的斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.75,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连错误也是伪装的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.25,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直至将死之前都在精心布局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.63,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是争抢王位的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:48.22,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵从想法与欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.73,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一次机会 在劫难逃的坏棋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.78,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最后机会 势必要击溃劲敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.77,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.71,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仅凭那种路数根本就无法追及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.85,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:06.25,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}将完全胜利紧握在手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.07,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有人都已望尘莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.76,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.77,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}そんな手じゃもう追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.99,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:06.90,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最初の一手で選ぶ 未知なるfuture
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:10.82,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その有り様 this way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:17.07,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後の一手で決める 世界のanswer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.05,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一人のwinner it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.58,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}この目は見据えた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:30.67,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰も未だ見通せぬ最適解を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:35.59,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全ては盤上支配するgame
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.21,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}思考の闘争
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.75,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Mistakeさえも偽装して
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.25,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Checkmateまで布石として
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.63,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kingを奪い合うgame
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:48.22,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}思想と欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.73,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}One chance 見逃さぬ悪手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.78,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Last chance 必ず仕留める
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.77,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.71,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}そんな手じゃもう追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.85,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:06.25,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全勝利はこの手の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.07,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰にももう追いつけない
